  <sect1 id="intro">
    <title>Introduction</title>
    <para>
      Disks can be broken up into chunks called partitions.  Often, each
      partition has its own purpose such as development partitions or download
      partitions.  Some people even make partitions for their music.
    </para>
  </sect1>
